              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5135245172655369034">We&apos;ve all heard the phrase &quot;Must See TV!&quot;, well this is the book equivalent to that phrase!! As a parent, how far would you go to protect your teenager? Is there a gray area?? To spy or not to spy? Is spying an invasion of privacy or a parent&apos;s right to know?? We, as parents, want to protect our children but where do we draw the line? Mike and Tia Baye feel the same way about their 16 year old son, Adam. They cross the line...or do they??<br/><br/>Another wonderfully crafted story by this author. Twists, </span>
  <span id="freeText5135245172655369034" style="display:none">We've all heard the phrase "Must See TV!", well this is the book equivalent to that phrase!! As a parent, how far would you go to protect your teenager? Is there a gray area?? To spy or not to spy? Is spying an invasion of privacy or a parent's right to know?? We, as parents, want to protect our children but where do we draw the line? Mike and Tia Baye feel the same way about their 16 year old son, Adam. They cross the line...or do they??<br /><br />Another wonderfully crafted story by this author. Twists, turns, suspense. Page-turning at it's best!</span>
